# EA Factory Core v1.0 — Frozen

EA Factory Core is complete (`ea-factory-core-v1.0`). See `docs/architecture/ea-factory-core-v1.md`.

## Frozen — treat as versioned APIs

Launcher, Orchestrator, Capability interface/Registry, ProjectContext, ArtifactService, WorkOrder, ProductionController, Builder Registry, Deliverable, Review Gates.

Do not redesign these. Do not add a new orchestration layer or framework pattern.

## Extend only via

- New **capabilities** (manifest + bootstrap + `canRun`/`execute`)
- New **builders** (Builder Registry)
- Append-only **artifacts / deliverables / review gates** with provenance

## Product work style

One capability or builder at a time → tests → logging → docs → stop for review.  
Optimize reliability, observability, performance, UX — not architecture.

## Definition of done

Founder launches from ChatGPT → research → discover → plan → build → QA → publish → notify → review-ready deliverable.
